📋 Day 16 – Kanban Board

📌 Project Overview
This project is a Kanban Board web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It helps users manage tasks visually by organizing them into different workflow stages.
The main goal of this project was to learn drag & drop functionality, DOM manipulation, and localStorage handling.

✨ Features

➕ Add new tasks
📦 Drag & drop tasks between columns
✏ Edit existing tasks
🗑 Delete tasks
💾 Save tasks using localStorage
🎨 Modern glassmorphism UI
📱 Responsive layout
⚡ Smooth hover & drag animations


🧱 Technologies Used

HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript (ES6+)


⚡ How It Works


User enters a task


JavaScript dynamically creates a task card


Tasks can be:

Dragged between columns
Edited
Deleted



localStorage saves all tasks automatically


Tasks remain after page refresh



